{"tid":2418574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<連燈誠實題> 正苦有非支那疫苗比你打，問心你會唔會狗衝？","createTime":"2021-02-22T17:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T17:27:17.000Z","uid":61766,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91ee7bfc5858ccb5dc27272597b9fa6a798f13b5","tid":2418574,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老閪都打咗先<br />\n<br />\n理據：<br />\n<br />\n個正苦無所不用其極，有非支那疫苗唔打咗先，遲啲搞強制注射/唔打無得出境或者返工，我咪焗打支那疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老閪都唔撚打，我寧願日日戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n理據：<br />\n<br />\n而家疫苗出世時間咁短，香港感染人數同死亡率都極低，老實講真係睇唔到要打疫苗嘅急切性，就算係鬼佬貨都係咁講。反之，疫苗出世未夠一年，副作用等等都未真係有足夠時間反映到，就咁睇，點計都係唔打穩陣好多喎。"},{"pid":"b22b7480c345c4299413eaafcf7aff421f6650e9","tid":2418574,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467e044df76228a9d6b9cae0dc1ee4ea162e7fc2","tid":2418574,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091dff4c7d6d70538fa602f7cec4b19ed7f3bdbf","tid":2418574,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008ed8f68b537902f41bade03567d8110d006646","tid":2418574,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"中聯辦嗰班都未打就問平民打唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b2bc51074e2095924de662fc94152a129acb5f","tid":2418574,"uid":361751,"like":1,"di